{"tid":511233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【割地兩檢】基本法18條仲有無效？譚惠珠：會有文件說明《基本法》不適用","createTime":"2017-12-27T09:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T15:33:38.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"14a84d365e4514edd3380cd2803d5e6b5c442818","tid":511233,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T09:23:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171227/57632286\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171227%2F57632286&d=odruODfeFYMtT7fookMWeQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=7513cacb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171227%2F57632286&h=4c855a80\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171227/57632286</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171227/large/1514364763_fe69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171227%2Flarge%2F1514364763_fe69.jpg&h=aae2184b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會今午全票通過，批准在高鐵西九龍站實施「一地兩檢」《合作安排》的決定草案，並指內地派駐口岸區的機構，會依照內地法律履行職責，範圍嚴格限制在內地口岸區之內，不同於《基本法》第18條，將全國性法律在整個香港實施的情況。有報道指，列席港區人大代表譚惠珠表示，將會有一份說明文件指基本法第18條不適用，而香港法庭須接受人大常委會的約束，不存在推翻人大常委會決定的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n《基本法》18條列明，只有被列入附件三的全國法律才在港適用，一地兩檢做法被指猶如「自閹」。人大通過草案後，據《now新聞》報道，譚惠珠稱，今午將會有「相當詳細說明」解釋一地兩檢的法律基礎及如何運作等，該文件會說明《基本法》不適用。"},{"pid":"1c567367ba05c4f530e55618ee8dd9a18490d419","tid":511233,"uid":38671,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T09:26:59.000Z","msg":"任你改，仲係法律？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0721b0ac1352f264a4cc36284b53b678f1c23e2f","tid":511233,"uid":47558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T09:28:57.000Z","msg":"基本法都不適用，咁有咩係適用<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25a80f3049b657f8983553a30dd63560e155679","tid":511233,"uid":47359,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T09:32:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會文件指出基本法第一條不適用?"},{"pid":"65cd06ea39cf026c886a3641f89f8ef68648de84","tid":511233,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T09:32:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會有文件指出基本法第一條不適用?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7354492a97184725bdee1539798365ae06dc0a2f","tid":511233,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8976cfa3a37a6fc416afb1da966453ce57e094","tid":511233,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a6596725b0b7f2d90934d2150c623e7918223d","tid":511233,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"任我改<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc40b2b41639b66abe65dcbca0c45420418359da","tid":511233,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T15:33:38.000Z","msg":"人大決定=法律 <br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}